he initial infectionThe tools the attackers deployed on the breached environment include the Cobalt Strike pen-test suite the AnyDesk and DameWare remote access tools network scanning utilities an AD database dumper and a Kerberos credentials stealerThis arsenal creates an attack profile that makes it very likely that the malware operators are interested in identifying accessible network points pivoting to other machines exfiltrating data and eventually deploying ransomware"
